      "id": "PopularPost263486",
      "post_content": "I rescind my previous comment in favour of the following: Flusterstorm prevents your opponent from countering your counter effectively, barring anti-storm effects of their own. It's kinda like a version of [Last Word](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Word) with a mana out, but considerably cheaper.",
      "posted_by": "LordRandomness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost263486\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I rescind my previous comment in favour of the following: Flusterstorm prevents your opponent from countering your counter effectively, barring anti-storm effects of their own. It's kinda like a version of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Last Word\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Word\">Last Word</a> with a mana out, but considerably cheaper.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '263486'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76236\">LordRandomness</span>\r\n                                (4/15/2013 4:01:20 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightCl